Riley always seems like a sweet girl to me... like almost has that Marylin Monroe curse of like, “I know what you want from me so fiiiiiiiine I’ll be that for you” (like how MM had to act like a ditzy dumb blonde bc of her beauty & sexiness, but really she was a deep, complex, artistic woman) but then when you actually get to hear her talk about stuff other than sex, or even sex but in a more thoughtful way instead of like “HOW BIG IS YOUR DICK?! (Lol), she comes off as really interesting and kind. I know she is a more sexual person, obviously, and that’s cool, as long as she gets to show that that’s not all she is. Even if only to a select few people. Cause I don’t think it would be mentally damaging as long as you had friends and loved ones who really did know you and see you for who you are.
Anyway, I’m sure we’d know by now if her & Jordan were dating since this was filmed a few months back, but I hope she finds a nice person who understands her job but also really loves and respects her. I’m sure Jordan will meet someone when he’s ready, he’s a catch.
